                <h2>6. Fenugreek (Methi) Seeds — Traditional Powerhouse</h2>
                <p>Methi dana Indian kitchen mein hamesha hota hai, aur ye <strong>hair fall ke liye bahut effective</strong> hai. Isme protein, nicotinic acid aur lecithin hota hai jo follicles strengthen karte hain.</p>

                <h3>Kaise Use Karein:</h3>
                <p>2 tablespoons methi seeds raat bhar paani mein bhigo dein. Subah grind karke paste banayein. Scalp pe lagayein, 30-40 minutes chhod dein. Mild shampoo se wash karein. Week mein 2 baar karein.</p>

                <h2>7. Amla (Indian Gooseberry) — Vitamin C Ka Raja</h2>
                <p>Amla mein orange se 20 guna zyada Vitamin C hota hai. Ye collagen production badhata hai, iron absorption improve karta hai, aur free radicals se follicles protect karta hai.</p>

                <h3>Use Karne Ke Tarike:</h3>
                <p><strong>Amla oil massage:</strong> Week mein 2 baar. <strong>Amla powder paste:</strong> Paani mein mix karke scalp pe lagayein, 20 minutes baad wash karein. <strong>Amla juice:</strong> Roz subah khali pet 2 tablespoons amla juice peeyein — inside-out approach.</p>

                <h2>Diet Changes — Andar Se Fix Karo</h2>
                <p>Natural remedies sirf bahar se kaam karti hain. Agar andar se nutrition nahi milega toh results limited honge. Ye <a href="vitamins-nutrition-healthy-hair.php">essential vitamins aur nutrients</a> daily diet mein hone chahiye:</p>

                <p><strong>Protein:</strong> Eggs, dal, paneer, chicken, fish — har meal mein protein zaroor hona chahiye. <strong>Iron:</strong> Palak, beetroot, dates, pomegranate, gur — especially women ke liye critical hai. <strong>Biotin:</strong> Almonds, walnuts, sweet potatoes, egg yolk. <strong>Zinc:</strong> Pumpkin seeds, chickpeas, yogurt. <strong>Omega-3:</strong> Flaxseeds, walnuts, fish. <strong>Vitamin C:</strong> Amla, orange, lemon — ye iron absorption 67% tak badha deta hai.</p>

                <h2>Lifestyle Habits Jo Hair Fall Naturally Reduce Karte Hain</h2>
                <p>Remedies aur diet ke saath kuch lifestyle changes bhi zaroori hain:</p>

                <p><strong>Sleep:</strong> Kam se kam 7-8 hours ki quality sleep lein. Sleep ke dauraan growth hormones release hote hain jo hair repair mein help karte hain. <strong>Stress management:</strong> Yoga, meditation, ya deep breathing daily karein. Chronic stress Telogen Effluvium ka sabse bada cause hai. <strong>Exercise:</strong> Regular exercise se blood circulation improve hota hai — scalp ko zyada nutrients milte hain. <strong>Hydration:</strong> 3-4 litre paani daily peeyein. Dehydrated body = brittle hair. <strong>Avoid chemicals:</strong> Sulfate-free shampoo use karein, heat styling minimize karein, aur chemical treatments se distance rakhein.</p>

                <p>Agar aap seriously <a href="how-to-grow-hair-faster-tips-that-actually-work.php">baal tez badhana chahte hain</a>, toh ye lifestyle changes remedies ke saath combine karein — results double honge.</p>

                <h2>Weekly Natural Hair Care Schedule</h2>
                <p>Confused hain ki kab kya karein? Ye simple weekly schedule follow karein:</p>

                <p><strong>Monday:</strong> Oil massage (coconut + rosemary) — raat ko lagayein. <strong>Tuesday:</strong> Gentle wash + green tea rinse. <strong>Wednesday:</strong> Aloe vera scalp treatment (45 min). <strong>Thursday:</strong> Rest day — sirf scalp massage (bina oil). <strong>Friday:</strong> Onion juice treatment (30 min) + wash. <strong>Saturday:</strong> Egg mask (30 min) + oil treatment raat ko. <strong>Sunday:</strong> Gentle wash + deep conditioning.</p>

                <p><strong>Daily:</strong> 5 min scalp massage, protein-rich diet, 3L paani, 7+ hours sleep.</p>

                <h2>Jab Natural Remedies Enough Na Hon — Clinical Backup</h2>
